name: GearUp
description: GearUp is a no-code and developer-friendly platform for building, testing, and deploying smart contracts. It combines AI and DeFi into an ecosystem called DeFAi, allowing users of any skill level to create secure smart contracts without writing code. It empowers secure, transparent blockchain automation for individuals and businesses alike.
